       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      *                                                        *
        PROGRAM-ID PGM3CC6D.
      **********************************************************
      *                                                        *
      *  ABRIL 2025  PROGRAMA CON DECLARACION DE ARCHIVOS      *
      *                                                        *
      **********************************************************
      *      MANTENIMIENTO DE PROGRAMA                         *
      **********************************************************
      *  FECHA   *    DETALLE        * COD *
      **************************************
      *23/10/2025*SUM SALDO A 'DU'   *     *
      *          *                   *     *
      *          *                   *     *
      *          *                   *     *
      *          *                   *     *
      **************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.

       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
             SELECT CLIENTE ASSIGN DDCLIENT
                    FILE STATUS IS WS-FILE-CLI.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD CLIENTE
            BLOCK CONTAINS 0 RECORDS
            RECORDING MODE IS F.

       01 R-CLIENTE      PIC X(50).


      **************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      **************************************
       77  FILLER        PIC X(26) VALUE '* INICIO WORKING-STORAGE *'.

       77  FILLER        PIC X(26) VALUE '* CODIGOS RETORNO FILES  *'.
       77  WS-FILE-CLI      PIC XX    VALUE SPACES.
      **************************************

       77  WS-STATUS-CLI    PIC X.
           88  WS-FIN-CLI             VALUE 'Y'.
           88  WS-NO-FIN-CLI         VALUE 'N'.

      **************************************
      *         LAYOUT SUCURSAL            *
      **************************************
           COPY CPCLI.

       77  WS-SUMA-SALDOS          PIC S9(12)V99 COMP-3 VALUE ZEROS.
       77  WS-TOTAL-DISP           PIC -$ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZZ.ZZ9,99
                                                        VALUE ZEROS.
       77  FILLER        PIC X(26) VALUE '* FINAL  WORKING-STORAGE *'.

      ***************************************************************.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
      **************************************
      *                                    *
      *  CUERPO PRINCIPAL DEL PROGRAMA     *
      *                                    *
      **************************************
       MAIN-PROGRAM.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO  THRU   F-1000-INICIO.

           PERFORM 2000-PROCESO  THRU  F-2000-PROCESO
                   UNTIL WS-FIN-CLI.

           PERFORM 9999-FINAL    THRU  F-9999-FINAL.

       F-MAIN-PROGRAM. GOBACK.

      **************************************
      *                                    *
      *  CUERPO INICIO APERTURA ARCHIVOS   *
      *                                    *
      **************************************
       1000-INICIO.
           SET WS-NO-FIN-CLI TO TRUE.

           OPEN INPUT  CLIENTE.


           IF WS-FILE-CLI IS NOT EQUAL '00'
              DISPLAY '* ERROR EN OPEN ARCHIVO CLIENTE = ' WS-FILE-CLI
              MOVE 9999 TO RETURN-CODE
              SET  WS-FIN-CLI     TO TRUE
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-LEER THRU F-2100-LEER.
       F-1000-INICIO.   EXIT.

      **************************************
      *                                    *
      *  CUERPO PRINCIPAL DE PROCESOS      *
      *                                    *
      **************************************
       2000-PROCESO.
           IF CLI-TIP-DOC = 'DU'
              ADD CLI-SALDO TO WS-SUMA-SALDOS
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-LEER THRU F-2100-LEER.
       F-2000-PROCESO. EXIT.

       2100-LEER.
           READ CLIENTE  INTO REG-CLIENTE

           EVALUATE WS-FILE-CLI
              WHEN '00'
                SET WS-NO-FIN-CLI  TO TRUE
              WHEN '10'
                SET WS-FIN-CLI  TO TRUE

              WHEN OTHER
                DISPLAY '* ERROR EN LECTURA CLIENTE = ' WS-FILE-CLI
                MOVE 9999 TO RETURN-CODE
                SET WS-FIN-CLI  TO TRUE

           END-EVALUATE.
       F-2100-LEER. EXIT.
      **************************************
      *                                    *
      *  CUERPO FINAL CIERRE DE FILES      *
      *                                    *
      **************************************
       9999-FINAL.

           IF RETURN-CODE = 9999
            CONTINUE
           ELSE
            CLOSE CLIENTE
            IF WS-FILE-CLI IS EQUAL '00'
               MOVE WS-SUMA-SALDOS TO WS-TOTAL-DISP
               DISPLAY 'TOTAL IMPORTE SUMADO PARA TIPO DE DOCUMENTO DU:'
               DISPLAY WS-TOTAL-DISP
            ELSE
               DISPLAY '* ERROR EN CLOSE ARCHIVO CLIENTE = '
                                            WS-FILE-CLI
               MOVE 9999 TO RETURN-CODE
               SET WS-FIN-CLI     TO TRUE
            END-IF


      **************************************
      *   MOSTRAR TOTALES DE CONTROL
      **************************************

           END-IF.

       F-9999-FINAL.
           EXIT.
      *
